  <div id="sub-plans" class="page">
    <section class="hero hero-small hero-sub-plans">
      <h1>PWCA Supplemental Unemployment Benefit Plan</h1>
      <p>Helping you support your workforce</p>
    </section>

    <section class="info-section">
      <h2>WHY CHOOSE THE SUB PLAN?</h2>
      <h3>PROTECT YOUR EMPLOYEES. IMPROVE YOUR BOTTOM LINE.</h3>
      <p>The PWCA Supplemental Unemployment Benefit (SUB) Plan allows employers to use fringe benefit dollars to fund tax-free income replacement for employees who experience involuntary job loss between government contracts or seasonal work.</p>
      <ul style="list-style:disc; padding-left:20px; max-width:650px; margin:0 auto 20px;">
        <li>Employees receive weekly benefits when out of work through no fault of their own.</li>
        <li>Employers reduce the need to pay out taxable fringe dollars as cash.</li>
        <li>You stay compliant with wage determinations under the Service Contract Act.</li>
      </ul>
      <div style="text-align:center; margin-top:40px;">
        <button class="btn-dark btn" onclick="showPage('contact')">GET IN TOUCH</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="info-section bg-light">
      <h2 style="text-align:left;">HOW IT WORKS</h2>
      <h3 style="text-align:left;">SIMPLE TO SET UP. EASY TO ADMINISTER.</h3>
      <div class="info-grid">
        <div>
          <p style="text-align:left;">The SUB Plan is a qualified benefit program under IRS guidelines. Contributions are made pre-tax, and employees receive tax-free benefits. SCA, Inc. handles all the administration — from compliance to claims management.</p>
          <ul style="text-align:left; list-style:disc; padding-left:20px;">
            <li>Employer allocates fringe dollars to the SUB Plan.</li>
            <li>SCA, Inc. manages the funds in a secure trust account.</li>
            <li>Employees who are laid off or between contracts can file a claim.</li>
            <li>Eligible employees receive weekly benefit payments tax-free.</li>
          </ul>
          <button class="btn" onclick="showPage('about')">ABOUT US</button>
        </div>
        <div class="info-image" aria-hidden="true">Profile Image</div>
      </div>
    </section>

